items.badge_description: Does the word picking favorites mean anything to you? Obviously not. That's 10 different beers in a row.
After a long day, what better way to kick back than with a crisp and refreshing lager? You're already feeling more relaxed, aren’t you?. That’s 5 different Lagers! Try 5 more to unlock Level 2.
It takes the perfect amount light, the right framing and a touch of creative love to get the perfect picture of your brew. Now it’s time to drink it! That’s 10 check-ins with a photo.

Fresh fish and crisp beer always hits the spot. Sit back, enjoy, and watch the sushi chefs work their magic. Kanpai! That's a beer at 5 different venues categorized as a Sushi Restaurant, Japanese Restaurant, Chinese Restaurant or Asian Restaurant. Try 5 more for Level 2!
